couchbackup
===========

Save / restore a single-server CouchDB data files. It will save:
- /var/lib/couchdb
- /etc/couchdb/vm.args (because the node name is important)

Save to a file
--------------

  ./couchbackup.sh $HOST dump /tmp/couchbackup.tar.gz

Restore from a file
-------------------

  ./couchbackup.sh $HOST load /tmp/couchbackup.tar.gz
